Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.68,0:00:17.06,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NChiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:22.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NChiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Rise and shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.19,0:00:27.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI] W-Wait!\NWho are you? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:30.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, well, you see--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:32.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Want me to donate\Nto your religion?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:33.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Or join some pyramid scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.95,0:00:35.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Too bad!\NI don't have any money!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:36.20,Main,,0,0,0,,No, we just--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI gasps]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:42.71,Main,,0,0,0,,We just want to\Nask you if we can be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:44.59,Main,,0,0,0,,If you wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:50.97,Main,,0,0,0,,[CHIYORI]\NSay what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.05,0:00:52.84,Main,,0,0,0,,This has gotta be\Nsome kind of trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:54.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.18,0:00:55.51,Main,,0,0,0,,There's no way anyone\Nwould wanna be friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.43,Main,,0,0,0,,with someone like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:00.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys are just\Ntrying to rob me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NOh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:06.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NWell, at least you tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.23,0:01:09.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:12.16,Main,,0,0,0,,This is never gonna work\Nif she doesn't trust us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:13.70,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NAh, just give her time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.78,0:01:15.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll come around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:18.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet she'll be all,\N"Yeah, let's all be friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.58,0:01:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,like you asked,\Nis that okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:23.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Something dumb like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.33,0:01:25.54,Main,,0,0,0,,This is really embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.63,0:01:27.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA] Well, when\Nthat finally happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:30.09,Main,,0,0,0,,just promise you'll treat\Nmy partner good, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:31.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.88,0:01:33.80,Main,,0,0,0,,See ya, card! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.89,0:01:36.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! You can just climb\Nout of a card that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.30,0:01:37.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[ELDORA]\NYep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:40.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you girls\Ntake care now, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.89,0:01:43.02,Main,,0,0,0,,--[ELDORA humming]\N--[RUKO] Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:53.78,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NEldora...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.86,Main,,0,0,0,,She really did love Chiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,That was so sweet of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not the only nice LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki's done so much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:02.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.45,0:02:03.75,Main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,And besides,\Nit's only natural isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:10.05,Main,,0,0,0,,We think of LRIGs\Nas tricking their Selectors,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:12.38,Main,,0,0,0,,but I realized something\Nwhen I became one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:14.80,Main,,0,0,0,,LRIGs are like any\Nother girl in this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:16.30,Main,,0,0,0,,They get hurt, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:18.39,Main,,0,0,0,,And some of them make\Nthe ultimate sacrifice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,for their Selectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Midoriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:24.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.94,Main,,0,0,0,,All of the girls who are\Ninvolved in these Battles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.02,0:02:27.44,Main,,0,0,0,,get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.98,Main,,0,0,0,,We're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.69,0:02:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] There is one girl who's\Ndifferent from all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.45,Main,,0,0,0,,That's Mayu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.53,0:02:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,She's jealous of\Nall the other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:43.62,Main,,0,0,0,,And that's why she crushes\Ntheir wishes the way she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:44.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.87,0:02:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I need you to take me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.92,0:02:49.38,Main,,0,0,0,,To Urith.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.89,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NConstruction's almost done,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:37.74,Main,,0,0,0,,and this is going to be\Nmy room, believe it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You weren't here\Nfor the fan event,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,but I fought against Ruko\Nin this very building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:49.00,Main,,0,0,0,,She was as beautiful\Nas she was powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:54.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You, on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.84,0:04:57.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the exact\Nopposite of Ruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Despite all of your tough talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:03.47,Main,,0,0,0,,you haven't been able\Nto kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NBut wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember\Nwhat you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:11.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)] And it wasn't just\Nher wish, but her very life
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.81,Main,,0,0,0,,that you snatched\Naway from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.40,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:21.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Please, that poor girl\Nwas dying when you battled her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:24.66,Main,,0,0,0,,--Some victory.\N--[AKIRA] I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:28.91,Main,,0,0,0,,It never mattered to me whether\Nthat girl was alive or dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Back then, a win was a win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I was so different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA sobbing]\NWhy? This thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,It's gonna make\Nmy face so ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.55,0:05:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 210A]\NWhat are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:49.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Now you look on the outside\Njust like you do on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.06,0:05:52.81,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the most disgusting\Nperson in the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:55.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[GIRL 210A]\NYou're worried about your face
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.11,0:05:59.78,Main,,0,0,0,,when your entire\Nsoul is twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.95,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:05.45,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NShe was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:09.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Every single thing about me\Nwas filthy and disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Yet, still,\Nyou took your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Instead of being repulsed,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,you reached down\Ndeep within my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:18.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I truly thought you were\Ntrying to save me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:22.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You like to\Nfind things of beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:25.18,Main,,0,0,0,,and break them into\Ntiny pieces, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You take things\Nthat are truly lovely
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:29.10,Main,,0,0,0,,and make them\Nfilthy and corrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,You used me to\Nget what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I was simply a pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Just a tool you used\Nto force Ruko to fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.73,0:06:38.73,Main,,0,0,0,,My, how surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.81,0:06:41.23,Main,,0,0,0,,And here I thought\Nyou were a hopeless idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I should've given\Nyou an inkling of credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:46.99,Main,,0,0,0,,So I suppose now you\Nwanna have your revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:49.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Though the odds of you\Ndoing so are laughable,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.62,Main,,0,0,0,,what do you hope to gain by\Nbeating me in a Selector battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you want\Nto see me ruined,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.08,Main,,0,0,0,,like you did the last Iona?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:57.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Or just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:06:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to put a scar on me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:02.21,Main,,0,0,0,,that would mirror the\Nnasty one you're sporting?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.22,Main,,0,0,0,,[AKIRA]\NBut I'll heal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.22,Main,,0,0,0,,The scar that I'll give you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.06,Main,,0,0,0,,It will be a pure\Nand beautiful wound
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.73,Main,,0,0,0,,inflicted on you\Nby my boundless love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But it's also that\Nsame deep, abiding love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:20.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I have for you that's\Ngonna heal that scar in turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.61,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll become an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.24,Main,,0,0,0,,And once I've turned back\Ninto a human again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.57,Main,,0,0,0,,the first thing that I'm\Ngonna do is track you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.65,0:07:29.78,Main,,0,0,0,,And then scar you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'll battle\Nagain for my wish,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.54,Main,,0,0,0,,and guess what\Nthat's gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,To heal your scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:38.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'll be\Nan LRIG again,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,and then a human,\Nand an LRIG after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:46.30,Main,,0,0,0,,And then every single time,\Nfrom here on out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna leave\Na scar on your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.93,Main,,0,0,0,,A physical reminder\Nof something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:58.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira Aoi's love for Urith.\NLike the last one I left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.73,Main,,0,0,0,,And see, by doing this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:01.52,Main,,0,0,0,,you won't be able to\Nsimply pull my strings
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.94,Main,,0,0,0,,and get rid\Nof me that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna leave a\Npermanent mark on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.36,0:08:09.49,Main,,0,0,0,,One that'll make sure\Nyou'll never forget me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.28,Main,,0,0,0,,[URITH (I)]\NYou're an interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:15.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.71,Main,,0,0,0,,All right.\NThen let's get to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:23.09,Main,,0,0,0,,If you're battle-hungry,\Nthen Tama and I are starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:26.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NRu... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:27.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,During that last battle, when\Nthose dark feelings came in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:35.22,Main,,0,0,0,,and took control of me,\NI had a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] If that wish\Ncould come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:38.43,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:41.56,Main,,0,0,0,,I'd do anything\Nto make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:44.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I make people cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:47.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:52.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You piece of shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:55.99,Main,,0,0,0,,[STAFF A]\NYou wanna see Iona?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:58.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Yes, it's important\Nwe speak with her right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey, I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You're Iona and\NAkira's friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,How's Iona's wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:07.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[STAFF B]\NHold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You mean you girls haven't\Nheard what happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:11.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.60,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE] A Battle put\NUrith in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.72,Main,,0,0,0,,That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:17.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] I'm getting\Na bad vibe from this, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I just hope that\NTama's okay and didn't get--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.48,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:27.15,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Yuzuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] A Battlefield\Njust opened up somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:30.53,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Can we find out\Nwho's battling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:36.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona, can you tell us\Nwhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:39.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It's strange,\Nbut I can't sense much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:42.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It's almost as if the battle\Nis being hidden by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:43.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Or by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:46.00,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO gasps]\NYou think it's--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.63,Main,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:53.01,Main,,0,0,0,,[panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.35,Main,,0,0,0,,[yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, Tama, now grow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,[BOTH gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.56,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NRu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.64,0:10:05.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Stay away, I don't want\Nyou to see me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:07.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:09.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Please don't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:27.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI] That shop sure had a\Ngood selection of singles, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.34,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)]\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.55,Main,,0,0,0,,[KAZUKI]\NYuzuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[car horn blares]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's go get\Nsomething to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:51.07,Main,,0,0,0,,You've been\Nacting strange lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:53.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You know that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,So that explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.49,0:11:01.41,Main,,0,0,0,,All those looks\Nyou've been giving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:02.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)] Since when\Nhave I been acting strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,A week ago?\NTwo weeks ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuzuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:09.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Who's better,\Nthe new me or the old me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Please be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:16.38,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NYes, I believe it's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NHey, wait, I just got a text!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,You did? From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't recognize the sender.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:39.99,Main,,0,0,0,,"If you want to\Nmeet Iona Urazoe..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.08,0:11:41.41,Main,,0,0,0,,"Head here."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:57.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NUrith! Urith!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:02.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Urith?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Where's Tama?\NLet me talk to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NThat email was very literal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.36,0:12:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:14.36,Main,,0,0,0,,This isn't Urith anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.44,0:12:16.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the real Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:19.74,Main,,0,0,0,,So you mean the first\None and not someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,using her body, the way\NUrith or an LRIG would?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA (REAL)]\NLrig.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA (REAL)]\NBeen awhile, hasn't it, Lrig?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:36.13,Main,,0,0,0,,How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.01,Main,,0,0,0,,We meet once again and\Nyou look just like me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? You just call her Lrig?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:43.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:45.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It's what I've\Nalways called her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:50.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NLRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.02,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA (REAL)]\NLrig?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's your name, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.61,0:12:57.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Not exactly, but I don't\Nhave one, so that'll do for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:58.86,Main,,0,0,0,,You're such a strange girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:01.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NSo what's your fondest wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Fondest wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.37,0:13:10.12,Main,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I wish I\Nwasn't Iona Urazoe anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You see, back then, everyone had\Nsuch high expectations of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:23.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I needed to not only live up\Nto the Urazoe name,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:26.89,Main,,0,0,0,,but also to my\Nresponsibilities as a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:29.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I had little time for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA (REAL)] The closest thing\NI had to a friend was Lrig.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:37.19,Main,,0,0,0,,She didn't say much\Nand I didn't ask much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,And amidst all the craziness,\NI found playing WIXOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.32,0:13:43.11,Main,,0,0,0,,to be relaxing, even fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Lrig and I battled\Nalongside each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.54,Main,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.38,Main,,0,0,0,,An Eternal Girl was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:00.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I went to the White Room,\Nmet Mayu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:02.88,Main,,0,0,0,,and found out\Nwhat had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NUnderstand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,You see what Selector\NBattles are all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.43,0:14:09.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:10.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.73,Main,,0,0,0,,All you have to do\Nis become an LRIG
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,and drag a Selector\Ninto Battle like I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA (REAL)]\NIt doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:23.07,Main,,0,0,0,,My wish to no longer be\NIona Urazoe already came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,So there's no reason\Nfor me to battle anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:28.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NWait...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.49,0:14:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't care about\Nbecoming a human again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Your life is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA (REAL)]\NYes. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:37.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NBut that's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.63,0:14:38.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA (REAL)]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NThat's not how it works!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me this is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me you want to become\Na human again no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:47.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me hear you scream\Nand wail for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:49.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Or else it's completely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Absolutely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.02,0:14:55.85,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA (REAL)]\NAnd then, I became an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:15:01.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, I was an\NLRIG for two other Selectors,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:04.45,Main,,0,0,0,,but knowing what I did, I\Nnever coerced them into Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:06.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:09.41,Main,,0,0,0,,They dreamt about\Ntheir wishes coming true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:12.37,Main,,0,0,0,,So they battled anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What's more, the Selectors\NI was paired with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,weren't suited for Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:18.63,Main,,0,0,0,,They lost every single one\Nthat they fought in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:22.59,Main,,0,0,0,,As a result of that,\Ntheir wishes were reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Mayu didn't like me very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.72,Main,,0,0,0,,That's why she did what she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.22,Main,,0,0,0,,It makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:31.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Why else would she assign me\Nas an LRIG to weaker girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.93,Main,,0,0,0,,She'd do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:36.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Honestly,\NI didn't care that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:39.94,Main,,0,0,0,,About myself, or even\Nabout the other girls, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.44,Main,,0,0,0,,With all the tears I've seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:43.94,Main,,0,0,0,,this game became\Nreally hard to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:47.32,Main,,0,0,0,,And then I felt\Nsomething strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,My real body...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.70,0:15:51.28,Main,,0,0,0,,This one, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:53.62,Main,,0,0,0,,It became so hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.29,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.37,0:15:57.71,Main,,0,0,0,,It was then I knew\Nwhat I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I needed to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:02.59,Main,,0,0,0,,If no one resided\Nin Iona Urazoe's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.38,Main,,0,0,0,,then my life\Nwould truly end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:06.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE gasps]\NI see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:09.05,Main,,0,0,0,,If Urith is no longer in\NIona's body, then that means--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.26,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NHer wish must have come true,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.35,0:16:11.85,Main,,0,0,0,,and an Eternal Girl was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:13.10,Main,,0,0,0,,This is complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like why the heck\Nis Iona's body hollow?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.89,Main,,0,0,0,,And if Urith became an LRIG,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:19.27,Main,,0,0,0,,then Tama should be a\Nhuman now, shouldn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:21.06,Main,,0,0,0,,And in Iona's real body, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:21.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:23.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Right, Iona?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, but Tama refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:28.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha--Refused?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodness, why didn't\Nyou become Iona Urazoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,No one would ever want to remain\Nas an LRIG, wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:44.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NYes, you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I sensed your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:47.88,Main,,0,0,0,,You want to be human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:50.59,Main,,0,0,0,,That way you can eat ice cream\Nwith Ru under the summer sun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.60,Main,,0,0,0,,and buy scrunchies together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:55.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I'm originally a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.56,Main,,0,0,0,,If I were to become one,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.27,Main,,0,0,0,,that means I'd have\Nto take someone's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.36,0:17:05.69,Main,,0,0,0,,They'd become an LRIG, and that\Ncould make them sad and lonely--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:07.82,Main,,0,0,0,,No more excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:09.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you I could\Nsense your feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:12.03,Main,,0,0,0,,So I know,\Nfor that wish of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:13.78,Main,,0,0,0,,you'd do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:17.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if that meant you had to\Nmake someone else miserable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:20.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA] Urith unleashed\Nthe bad version of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:23.84,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want that me\Nto come out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA gasps]\NBut Ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.46,Main,,0,0,0,,I can sense her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,She's still looking\Neverywhere for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:32.55,Main,,0,0,0,,even after what\Nhappened last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:33.68,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though I wish\NI could be with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru'll never\Nbe able to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:40.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Because the bad Tama\Nisn't the same Tama
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.85,0:17:43.44,Main,,0,0,0,,that Ru knows and loves!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,And that's why I\Nwon't become a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:49.28,Main,,0,0,0,,because I can't let Ru find me,\Neven if it breaks my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:52.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru and I were friends,\Nbut we can't ever be again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:53.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:55.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I broke the promise\NI made to her
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:59.12,Main,,0,0,0,,so that her wish\Ncould come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] The thing is,\NI have a wish to fight for!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It's to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You and Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:08.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Plus everyone else\Nwho became LRIGs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll see! I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll bring you all\Nback to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:15.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NThat's Ru's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna do whatever it\Ntakes to make it come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.11,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA (REAL)]\NThanks for walking me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:30.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been a pleasure.\NBe safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.49,Main,,0,0,0,,You do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] This might be\Nweird coming from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.82,Main,,0,0,0,,but no more\NSelector Battles, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:39.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Never again, understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:42.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Um... Anything to add, Iona?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:45.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:48.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, I have to\Ngive you credit, Lrig.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:51.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It seems you've grown up\Na bit since last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:54.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:56.47,Main,,0,0,0,,And I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:06.52,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NTama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.44,Main,,0,0,0,,She's with Mayu now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:14.90,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Just when we decide\Nto talk to Mayu, this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:17.62,Main,,0,0,0,,That plan's shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:18.74,Main,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:20.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:22.20,Main,,0,0,0,,I think the only thing\Nthat's changed is the order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Our plan was to get\Nher out of that room,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.92,Main,,0,0,0,,and then to convince her\Nto stop all these battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.00,0:19:29.09,Main,,0,0,0,,But now I just need\Nto win a few of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:32.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll become an LRIG and get\Ntransported to the White Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:33.92,Main,,0,0,0,,To where Mayu and Tama are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Once I'm there,\NI'm sure I can get Mayu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.68,0:19:37.68,Main,,0,0,0,,to change her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:39.55,Main,,0,0,0,,That's too dangerous,\NRuko, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:41.47,Main,,0,0,0,,But we have to\Nget to her somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:42.47,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NAre you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:44.27,Main,,0,0,0,,You can't face her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:46.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NDon't worry, she won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Iona.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:54.94,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NWait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.03,0:19:56.57,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:58.57,Main,,0,0,0,,We've been calling\Nher "Iona" all this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:01.37,Main,,0,0,0,,but that was never even\Nher name in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:03.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh. Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:04.58,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NI'm fine with "Iona."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.54,Main,,0,0,0,,No way!\NLet's come up with new name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,We can think\Nof something. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:15.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure thing! What should it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.09,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there any word\Nthat's your favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Yeah, like how\NChiyori's was "Chorizo"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,and she said she\Nwanted to be called that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.56,Main,,0,0,0,,when she became an LRIG.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:25.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:29.27,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NIt's snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.91,0:20:42.87,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO, HITOE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NMy favorite thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.83,Main,,0,0,0,,That's it. It's snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:53.25,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NBack in that room with Mayu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:55.42,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NShut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:57.21,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:21:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NShut up. Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:03.76,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA] We could never venture\Ninto the outside world,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.85,0:21:07.14,Main,,0,0,0,,but we could still\Nhear it through our walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:10.06,Main,,0,0,0,,But sometimes it was silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NThe snow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:18.57,Main,,0,0,0,,...took away all of those sounds\Nwe didn't want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:22.07,Main,,0,0,0,,It was as if it\Nerased the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:26.91,Main,,0,0,0,,The snow was cold, yet kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Snow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:32.25,Main,,0,0,0,,What about "Yuki"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:34.04,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NYeah, "Yuki" means "snow"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.13,0:21:36.17,Main,,0,0,0,,and it's really pretty, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.21,Main,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:39.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's the\Nperfect name, Ruko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:41.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"Yuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:44.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I like that. "Yuki."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:45.43,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI] Now we don't\Nhave to say "LRIG Iona"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:47.39,Main,,0,0,0,,and "human Iona" or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh, darn, it totally\Nslipped my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:52.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I meant to ask Iona about\Nwho sent us that text
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.44,Main,,0,0,0,,that told us\Nwhere to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.61,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO]\NOh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, geez, that was\Nreally stupid of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:21:59.82,Main,,0,0,0,,[IONA]\NIs there an e-mail address?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,[HITOE]\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:04.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like their handle\Nis "Shadow Prince."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.12,0:22:06.24,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Do you guys know\Nanyone who goes by that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:07.41,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,[YUZUKI]\NUm, yeah. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:18.17,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NShiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:19.92,Main,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.51,0:22:24.13,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NKuro is the bad girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:26.43,Main,,0,0,0,,And you're the good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:27.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.06,0:22:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You're far more\Nspiteful than she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:32.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Spiteful? I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:34.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:36.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You're like a beautiful rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:39.98,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU]\NBut one with thorns!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:41.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You cut me deeply!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:42.99,Main,,0,0,0,,And leave me alone\Nhere to wither!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:44.07,Main,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.91,0:22:50.74,Main,,0,0,0,,[MAYU] So now I've decided\Nto lock you away for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.83,0:22:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.37,0:22:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Why did I let you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.75,0:22:55.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I never will again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:22:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NNo, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.05,0:23:01.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Ru!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:04.84,Main,,0,0,0,,[TAMA]\NRu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:20.65,Main,,0,0,0,,[HANAYO (Y)]\NWelcome back, Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:43.80,Main,,0,0,0,,You're so incredibly stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Your wish is never\Ngoing to come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:50.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.93,0:23:53.39,Main,,0,0,0,,[RUKO] Next time:\N"That Locked Window."
